  "description": "A breathtaking aerial view of a sprawling city at night, illuminated by countless lights. The scene is dominated by a dense network of streets and buildings, creating a dazzling display of urban luminescence. Long, brightly lit avenues cut through the cityscape, resembling glowing rivers. The buildings vary in height, with some skyscrapers rising prominently above the surrounding structures. In the distant background, a bridge is faintly visible, connecting different parts of the urban landscape. The overall impression is one of vastness, energy, and the vibrant life of a major metropolitan area.",
